data.description: Come and see this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bath CALI model in HOLLY ESTATES in beautiful Mt. Dora!! This home is ready for its new owner. This home features 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. It has an open-concept living space that's just right for the needs and comfort of your family. The kitchen is open to the family room. It offers a large separate island with many preparation surfaces and a breakfast bar for meals or snack time. The dining room size allows you to choose a 4 or 6-seater table. If you need space, this home has exactly what you want. Everyone will enjoy their separate space to relax, read, learn, and play games ....the owner's suite offers a walk-in closet, linen closet, private water closet, walk-in shower, and dual sinks. The owner's suite is tucked away from the other bedrooms. It offers privacy and a large en suite bathroom with double vanity sinks, a walk-in closet, and storage space. The backyard is enclosed for your pets or if you like to entertain and have friends and family over. Holly Estates has a low HOA, and amenities include a swimming pool for those hot Florida days when it's time to relax and play with friends and family, plus a playground, exercise/stretching stations, and a soccer field. The community is close to the 429 expressway, making for an easy commute to Orlando. Holly Estates is just a short drive to downtown Mount Dora and the Reningers Antiques & Market Place. Enjoy nearby shopping and dining, all within reach. Make your appointment today, and don't miss this home!!
